data.description:
Huntleigh Ridge Dream Home! Move-in Ready & Primed for Fun!

This 2021 stunner in Estates at Huntleigh Ridge ticks all the boxes: top-rated Wentzville schools, bright open floor plan, and contemporary finishes (hello, quartz countertops!). Whip up meals in the chef-worthy kitchen, unwind in the spa-like master retreat with whirlpool tub and separate shower, and gather loved ones in the spacious living area. Need more room? The full basement begs to be your future rec space or massive 4th bedroom. Three more bedrooms, 2 full baths, laundry just off the kitchen, and a 3-car garage complete the picture. Plus, newer appliances and washer/dryer stay! Move in, unpack, and start making memories. Don't miss your chance - this gem won't last!
